<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7624113>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4A–H. Gongylonema bettongiae sp. nov. A, Cephalic end female, en face view. B, Anterior end holotype male, ventrolateral view. C, Excretory pore, lateral view. D, Posterior end holotype male, lateral view. E, Left spicule tip with membranous terminal ending. F, Right spicule tip with membranous terminal ending. G. Gubernaculum accommodating both right and left spicules. H, Posterior end female, ventral view. Scale bars: Figs. 4A, 4E, 4F = 20 µm. Figs. 4B–4D, 4G, 4H = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7624113/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

